COMPILING INSTRUCTIONS
**********************
First, follow the instructions for server.py,
and then complete the instructions for client.c.
----------------------
server.py
----------------------
1) Compiling:
	chmod +x server.py
2) Running:
	./server.py [port number]
3) Next, follow prompts.
4) Type "\quit" to exit the chat
----------------------
client.c
----------------------
1) Compiling:
	gcc -Wall client.c -o client
2) Running:
	./client [flip#] [port number]
3) Next, follow prompts.
4) Type "\quit" to exit the chat